      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">旱麓.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>瞻彼旱麓，榛楛濟濟。豈弟君子，干祿豈弟。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Look at the foot of the Han,
How abundantly grow the hazel and arrow-thorn.
Easy and self-possessed was our prince,
In his pursuit of dignity (still) easy and self-possessed.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-005__002__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
