      <prop type="x-source-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·005.2</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">旱麓.2</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>瑟彼玉瓚，黃流在中。豈弟君子，福祿攸降。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Massive is that libation-cup of jade,
With the
​yellow liquid sparkling in it.
Easy and self-possessed was our prince,
The fit recipient of blessing and dignity.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-005__003__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
