      <prop type="x-target-segment-count">1</prop>
      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·005.3</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">旱麓.3</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鳶飛戾天，魚躍于淵。豈弟君子，遐不作人。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>The hawk flies up to heaven,
The fishes leap in the deep.
Easy and self-possessed was our prince:—
Did
he not exert an influence on men?</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-005__004__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
