      <prop type="x-translation-ref">旱麓.5</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>瑟彼柞棫，民所燎矣。豈弟君子，神所勞矣。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Thick grow the oaks and the buckthorn,
Which the people use for fuel.
Easy and self-possessed was our prince,
Cheered and encouraged by the spirits.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
    <tu tuid="shijing__daya-wenwang-005__006__zhwikisource-20260530__legge-sbe-v3-1879">
