      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·大雅·文王之什·005.6</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">旱麓.6</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>莫莫葛藟，施于條枚。豈弟君子，求福不回。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Luxuriant are the dolichos and other creepers,
Clinging to the branches and stems.
Easy and self-possessed was our prince,
Seeking for happiness by no crooked ways.</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
